    "description": "《残秽的我们》是一款本土手绘写实风格的恐怖冒险游戏，以真实事件为蓝本改编。在游戏中，玩家将跟随女主“无者”的脚步，深入由亡者怨念而产生的“怨秽地”，利用“刻印”的力量，探究隐藏其中的一段真实往事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/0d8c7bc2966c67aa541d313ecb368601.avif?t=1670591468\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>人如果带着强烈的怨念死去，<br><br>便会在其身亡之处，产生名为“怨秽地”的空间。<br><br>亡者会化为虚无的灵魂，忘却生前种种，盲目徘徊于其中，无法转生。<br><br>生者若误入此处，便会在具象污秽的折磨下痛苦死去，其灵魂将成为滋养“怨秽地”的养料。<br><br>随着养料的增多，“怨秽地”也会一同扩大，以便吞噬更多的灵魂。<br><br>唯有“无者”，可除污秽。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/e3a752d08bab9e9a558b319febaca9d1.poster.avif?t=1670591468\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/e3a752d08bab9e9a558b319febaca9d1.webm?t=1670591468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/e3a752d08bab9e9a558b319febaca9d1.mp4?t=1670591468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/0f92a78337528a1f7902c0c21c3c43d5.avif?t=1670591468\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>游戏以纯手绘写实风格，还原了一段跨度长达数十年的真实往事。<br><br>恐怖并不局限于外在的表现，深入内心的幽邃，会让你不寒而栗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/11ddb87b009b6a7c6d29615510f108fd.poster.avif?t=1670591468\" width=618 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/11ddb87b009b6a7c6d29615510f108fd.webm?t=1670591468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/11ddb87b009b6a7c6d29615510f108fd.mp4?t=1670591468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/dfb51927927195bdf1bf5a69242802d1.avif?t=1670591468\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>游戏中的每一个角色，都曾经鲜活的存在于这个世界上。<br><br>也许你也能从中找到熟悉的影子。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/b641c9620534e7722dd97dad8b68ab35.avif?t=1670591468\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>不仅仅是贴合剧情的解密。<br><br>“怨秽地”中还潜伏着更恐怖的东西。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/aa56d356ad859b5dbe4be965a410ab36.poster.avif?t=1670591468\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/aa56d356ad859b5dbe4be965a410ab36.webm?t=1670591468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788170/extras/aa56d356ad859b5dbe4be965a410ab36.mp4?t=1670591468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏一共包含四个章节，每章都是一个完整的故事，全部取材于真实事件，独立却又有关联。<br><br>同时，“无者”又从何而来？这一切也在等你找寻答案。<br><br>本次发布为游戏的第一章。",
